\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4 Out of these few simple rules an immense amount of potential patterns can be displayed. It all depends on the starting conditions. Each of which can lead to a variety different end results over just a few iterations, even from extremely similar initial conditions. Some of the patterns may lead nowhere, while others may create very stable patterns that continue over many generations.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4 \tab This is something you will quickly realize within Tricking. Once you understand a few of the rules to operate within, entire worlds of complexity are immediately opened up to be investigated. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s this feature that really hooks us. We don\u8217\'92t have to learn all of Tricking to really engage with this system. We can choose to find the areas that excite us about it the most and spend the majority of our time within those areas. Exploring it in a way that only we can. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4 That is the magic that lies just beyond that barrier to entry. Rich worlds of complexity and emergence from simple rules. For those of us who do make it past that barrier, lifetimes worth of exploration can be found.       And once they are found they grab hold of our interest and set us on a new path.}
